<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Zipicka</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="./logo.png" type="image/x-icon">
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <!-- Font Awesome CDN -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" />

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/cart.css">

</head>

<body>
  <div id="navbar-container">
        <%- include('navbar') %>
    </div>
  <div class="container-fluid py-5" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);">
    <div class="row">
      <!-- Center: Main Image -->
      <div class="main_img col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-12 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-3">
        <img src="" alt="Main Image" class="gallery-main" id="main-image" />
      </div>

      <!-- Right Side: Product Details -->
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-12 product-details p-3 bg-transparent">
        <h4>TA-105 Universal Travel Adapter</h4>
        <span>$22.99</span>
        <p>
          Global Compatibility: All-in-one adapter includes 4 different plugs that adapt to 200+ countries & regions.
          Versatile Charging: Say goodbye to tangled cords and limited outlets. Our adapter allows you to charge up to 6
          devices at once.
          Customer Trust: Over 1 million satisfied customers and recommended by 20+ major media outlets and 10K+ 5-star
          reviews.
          Safety & Security: Cruise friendly. This travel adapter is equipped with built-in 8A fuse, safety shutters and
          plug lock system. In addition, it is certified by RoHS, CE, and FCC, ensuring its safety and reliability.
          Note：Our adapter does NOT convert voltage, you must make sure that the AC-powered device you intend to use
          abroad
          supports dual voltage (with"100-240V, 50/60Hz" specs printed on it).
        </p>

        <!-- FAQ Section -->
        <ul class="faq p-0">
          <div class="faq-item mb-3">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(1)">
              <span>Specification</span>
              <i id="icon-1" class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="answer-1">
              <p><strong>AC Input:</strong> 100-240V~, 50-60Hz</p>
              <p><strong>AC Output:</strong> 100-240V~, 8A Max</p>
              <p><strong>Max Power:</strong>880W at 110V~, 1920W at 240V~</p>
              <p><strong>USB-A Output:</strong>5V⎓ 2.4A</p>
              <p><strong>USB-C Output:</strong> 5V⎓ 3A</p>
              <p><strong>Total DC Output:</strong>5V⎓ 5.6A, 28W</p>
              <p><strong>Product Weight:</strong>5.1 oz</p>
              <p><strong>Color:</strong> Black, White, Rose Gold, Space Grey</p>
              <p><strong>Product Dimension:</strong>Product Dimension:</p>
              <strong>Packing List:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li>1* TA-105 Travel Adapter </li>
                <li>1* Carry Bag</li>
                <li>2* Extra Spare 8A Fuses in A Pouch </li>
                <li>
                  1* User Manual</li>
              </ul>



            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item mb-3">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(2)">
              <span>User manual</span>
              <i id="icon-2" class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="answer-2">
              <header>
                <h2>Travel Adapter User Manual</h2>
            </header>
            
            <section>
                <h4>1. Introduction</h4>
                <p>Thank you for purchasing our universal travel adapter. This manual will guide you through the usage, features, and safety instructions to ensure optimal performance and safety during use.</p>
            </section>
        
            <section>
                <h4>2. Package Contents</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>Universal Travel Adapter</li>
                    <li>Carrying Pouch</li>
                    <li>User Manual</li>
                </ol>
            </section>
        
            <section>
                <h4>3. Features</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>Supports worldwide plug types (US, EU, UK, AU).</li>
                    <li>Built-in dual USB ports for charging devices.</li>
                    <li>Compact, lightweight, and portable design.</li>
                    <li>Safety shutter and fuse protection.</li>
                </ol>
            </section>
        
            <section>
                <h4>4. How to Use</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>Identify the plug type required for your destination.</li>
                    <li>Slide out the appropriate plug using the selector switches.</li>
                    <li>Connect the adapter to a power outlet.</li>
                    <li>Plug your device into the adapter socket.</li>
                    <li>Ensure the voltage compatibility of your device (100V-240V).</li>
                </ol>
            </section>
        
            <section>
                <h4>5. Safety Instructions</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>Do not use the adapter with high-power appliances like hairdryers or irons.</li>
                    <li>Ensure your device supports the local voltage before plugging in.</li>
                    <li>Keep the adapter away from water or damp environments.</li>
                    <li>Unplug the adapter when not in use.</li>
                    <li>Do not disassemble or modify the adapter.</li>
                </ol>
            </section>
        
            <section>
                <h4>6. Troubleshooting</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Problem:</strong> Device not charging.<br>
                        <strong>Solution:</strong> Check if the adapter is properly connected and your device is compatible with the local voltage.</li>
                    <li><strong>Problem:</strong> Adapter overheats.<br>
                        <strong>Solution:</strong> Disconnect immediately and let it cool down before reusing.</li>
                </ol>
            </section>
        
            <section>
                <h4>7. Warranty Information</h4>
                <p>This travel adapter comes with a one-year warranty. Please retain your proof of purchase for warranty claims.</p>
            </section>
        
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item mb-3">
            <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(3)">
              <span>Shipping return and warranty</span>
              <i id="icon-3" class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="answer-3">
              <header>
                <h3>Shipping and Warranty Information</h3>
            </header>
            
            <section>
                <h2>Shipment</h2>
                <p>All orders are processed within 1-2 business days. Customized products with quantities of less than 10 will take approximately 3 business days to produce.</p>
                
                <h3>United States</h3>
                <p>Free U.S. shipping on orders over $9.99. Expedited shipping is available for an additional fee. Enjoy a 30-day hassle-free return policy and a 90-day free exchange policy.</p>
                
                <h3>Canada</h3>
                <p>Shipping costs include customs duties by default and delivery in 10-15 business days. No free returns; refunds are based on return shipping costs. For orders over $120, please contact Support.</p>
                
                <h3>EU Countries</h3>
                <p>Shipping costs include customs duties by default and delivery in 3-7 business days. No free returns; refunds are based on return shipping costs. Contact Support for orders over $200 (EU) or $361 (Germany).</p>
                
                <h3>Customized Products</h3>
                <p>Custom products cannot be returned unless there is a defect or quality issue with the product.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section>
                <h2>Warranty</h2>
                <p>All Zipicka products come with a 2-year limited warranty. This warranty covers defects in materials and workmanship under normal use conditions.</p>
            </section>
        
            </div>
          </div>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom: Thumbnail Gallery -->
      <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center gap-2 flex-wrap mt-4">
        <img src="/img//g6.jpg" alt="Thumbnail 1" class="gallery-thumbnail active-thumbnail" />
        <img src="/img//g11.jpg" alt="Thumbnail 2" class="gallery-thumbnail" />
        <img src="/img//g3.jpg" alt="Thumbnail 3" class="gallery-thumbnail" />
        <img src="/img//g4.jpg" alt="Thumbnail 4" class="gallery-thumbnail" />
        <img src="/img//g6.jpg" alt="Thumbnail 5" class="gallery-thumbnail" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- Shopping Cart Section -->
  <section class="h-100 h-custom">
    <div class="container h-100 py-5">
      <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-100">
        <div class="col">

          <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" class="h5">Travel Adopter</th>
                  <th scope="col">Format</th>
                  <th scope="col">Quantity</th>
                  <th scope="col">Price</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody id="cart-items">
                <!-- Cart items will be dynamically added here -->
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>


          <!-- Checkout Section -->
          <div class="card shadow-2-strong mb-5 mb-lg-0" style="border-radius: 16px;">
            <div class="card-body p-4">
              <!-- Payment Methods -->
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 col-xl-3 mb-4 mb-md-0">
                  <form id="payment-form">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-row pb-3">
                      <div class="d-flex align-items-center pe-2">
                        <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="paymentMethod" id="credit-card"
                          value="Credit Card" aria-label="..." checked />
                      </div>
                      <div class="rounded border w-100 p-3">
                        <p class="d-flex align-items-center mb-0">
                          <i class=""></i> Credit Card
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-row pb-3">
                      <div class="d-flex align-items-center pe-2">
                        <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="paymentMethod" id="paypal" value="PayPal"
                          aria-label="..." />
                      </div>
                      <div class="rounded border w-100 p-3">
                        <p class="d-flex align-items-center mb-0">
                          <i class="fab fa-cc-paypal fa-2x fa-lg text-body pe-2"></i> PayPal
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </form>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 col-xl-6">
                  <!-- Card Details -->
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 col-xl-6">
                      <div class="form-outline mb-4">
                        <input type="text" id="card-name" class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="ANEES MIR"
                          oninput="validateCardName()" />
                        <label class="form-label" for="card-name">Name on Card</label>
                      </div>
                      <div class="form-outline mb-4">
                        <input type="text" id="expiry-date" class="form-control form-control-lg"
                          oninput="validateExpiryDate()" placeholder="MM/YY" />
                        <label class="form-label" for="expiry-date">Expiration Date</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-xl-6">
                      <div class="form-outline mb-4">
                        <input type="text" id="card-number" class="form-control form-control-lg"
                          placeholder="1111 2222 3333 4444" maxlength="16" oninput="validateCardNumber()" />
                        <label class="form-label" for="card-number">Card Number</label>
                      </div>
                      <div class="form-outline mb-4">
                        <input type="password" id="cvv" class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="CVV"
                          maxlength="3" />
                        <label class="form-label" for="cvv">CVV</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-xl-3">
                  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between" style="font-weight: 500;">
                    <p class="mb-2">Subtotal</p>
                    <p class="mb-2" id="subtotal">$0.00</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between" style="font-weight: 500;">
                    <p class="mb-0">Shipping</p>
                    <p class="mb-0" id="shipping">$2.99</p>
                  </div>
                  <hr class="my-4">
                  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-4" style="font-weight: 500;">
                    <p class="mb-2">Total (tax included)</p>
                    <p class="mb-2" id="total">$0.00</p>
                  </div>
                  <button type="button" id="checkout-btn" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                      <span>Checkout</span>
                      <span id="total-price">$0.00</span>
                    </div>
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OTP Modal -->
  <div class="modal" tabindex="-1" id="otp-modal">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title">Enter OTP</h5>
          <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <input type="text" id="otp-input" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter OTP" />
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" id="otp-submit-btn" class="btn btn-primary">Submit OTP</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- feedback  -->
  <div class="container feedback mb-3">
    <!-- Top Section -->
    <div class="top d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-center justify-content-center text-center flex-wrap">
      <!-- Heading -->
      <h3 class="mb-2 w-100">Leave Your Feedback</h3>

      <!-- Star Rating -->
      <div class="stars justify-content-center my-2 w-100">
        <input type="radio" id="star5" name="rating" class="star" value="5" />
        <label class="star" for="star5"></label>

        <input type="radio" id="star4" name="rating" class="star" value="4" />
        <label class="star" for="star4"></label>

        <input type="radio" id="star3" name="rating" class="star" value="3" />
        <label class="star" for="star3"></label>

        <input type="radio" id="star2" name="rating" class="star" value="2" />
        <label class="star" for="star2"></label>

        <input type="radio" id="star1" name="rating" class="star" value="1" />
        <label class="star" for="star1"></label>
      </div>

      <!-- Average Rating -->
      <h4 id="average-rating" class="mb-0 mx-2 w-100">5</h4>
      <p id="feedback-count" class="mb-0 mx-2 w-100">(0)</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feedback Form -->
    <form id="feedback-form" class="m-3">
      <div class="form-group mb-2">
        <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Your Name" required class="form-control" />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group mb-2">
        <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Your Email" required class="form-control" />
      </div>
      <textarea id="feedback" rows="4" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="Leave your feedback..."
        required></textarea>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary px-4 py-2 mx-auto d-block" id="checkout-bt">Submit Feedback</button>
    </form>

    <!-- Feedback Container -->
    <div class="container py-4">
      <div class="row g-3" id="feedback-container">
        <!-- Feedback items will be dynamically inserted here -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>






  <div id="footer-container">
    <%- include('footer') %> <!-- EJS partial for footer -->
  </div>




  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>

  <!-- Slick JavaScript -->

  <script src="/js/code.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/cart.js"></script>
</body>

</html>